{"tid":2125613,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"性命不可貴，清譽價更高。所以我還是自己花錢買口罩。 李純恩","createTime":"2020-07-26T09:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T09:46:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b780bf7a37a628302ed15c399fcb0e9d0b6c12b3","tid":2125613,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:45:25.000Z","msg":"性命不可貴，清譽價更高。所以我還是自己花錢買口罩。 李純恩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9/daily/article/20200726/20963282/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25B4%2594%25E6%2581%25A9%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200726%2F20963282%2F&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=21a6cb24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25B4%2594%25E6%2581%25A9%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200726%2F20963282%2F&h=99114f4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9/daily/article/20200726/20963282/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n又要買口罩 - 李純恩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200726/large/1595663494_89fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200726%2Flarge%2F1595663494_89fb.jpg&h=479faefa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n半年前疫情剛令人緊張，到處鬧口罩荒的時候，有沒有口罩成了一種「貧富差距」，家裏有幾盒口罩，可以拿出來「炫富」。那時候只要有得買便大手入貨，出外旅行，買口罩買消毒用品更成了一個旅途節目，藥店如景點，一看到就鑽進去。<br />\n<br />\n於是家裏儲了許多口罩，看着都覺得人來瘋。以二○○三年的經驗，覺得這口罩必然是用不光的，一定會像今年在家中發現還有○三年口罩存貨一樣，多出來的口罩就會存下去，如無意外，這輩子家裏都不用再買口罩。但世事難料，想不到瘟神沖不走，抗疫的戰綫越拉越長，曠日持久，一日一罩，消耗極快，這天竟然要為家中口罩補貨了。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。朋友說你們香港人不是都有政府派發的一用可以用六十次的口罩嗎？一隻可用六十天，要準備那麼多幹什麼？  我說。。。。。。。。。。。。。性命不可貴，清譽價更高。所以我還是自己花錢買口罩。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李純恩<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"e0d44931e4f303ca1cb68029d30148e783eca0d6","tid":2125613,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}